quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  9,118,"[O ja…ďanii tuubuubuyee on] kadi …ďeen tato luutndioo…ďe, haa leydi ndin faa…óani …ďe e hoore ko ndi yaaji kon; woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďittanii…ďe, …ďe fellitii won de moolorde e Alla aalaa si wanaa ka makko. refti o hawrindini …ďe e tuubuubuyee fii yo …ďe tuubu. Pellet, ko Alla woni ja…ďoowotuubabuya, jurmotoo…óo."
  9,119,"Eeymon gooŇč…óii…ďe, kulee Alla laatodon e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen."
  9,120,"Haananaa yim…ďe Madiina …ďeen, e …ďeen won…ďe sera ma…ď…ďe immorde e yim…ďe ladde …ďen, nde …ďe luttitata …ďaawo Nulaa…óo Alla on, wanaa nde …ďe yi…óatanta ko'e ma…ď…ďe …ďura mo.Ko wa…ói, noon ko he…ďataa …ďe, wanaa tampere, wanaa heege fii laawol Alla ngol, …ďe tippataa(yabbatah) e nokkuure tikkinaynde heefer…ďe …ďeen, …ďe kawrataa e ga√Īo hawrannde, si wanaa …ďe mbinndante e …óuum gollal mo∆ī∆īal. Pellet, Alla yeebataako njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  9,121,"∆Āe wintotaako(nafqatah) wintaari, fam…óundi maa mawnundi, …ďe ta∆īataa aynde(joolol)=caatngol, si wanaa …ďe mbinndante …óuum, fii yo Alla yo…ď …ďe ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko …ďe ngollaynoo."
  9,122,"Haananaa gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen nde …ďe njahata (jihaadi) …ďe fof ma…ď…ďe. Ko ha…óno fedde kala e ma…ď…ďe yalta fii yo …ďe faamino ka diina, e fii yo …ďe jeertin yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe si …ďe nduttitike e ma…ď…ďe, mbelejo'o, kam…ďe …ďe ndeentoto."